data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this splendid condo with a spacious open floor plan. This two-bedroom gem close to local colleges and offers a cozy ambiance with gas fireplace in the living room, creating the ideal setting for relaxation and gatherings. The first floor boasts a half bath for your guests' convenience, making entertaining a breeze. Kitchen offers plenty of counter space. Upstairs, you'll find two generously sized bedrooms, ensuring peaceful retreats at days end. The second bedroom offers flexibility for a home office or guest room. Laundry and the main bathroom are conveniently located near the bedrooms. The lower level surprises with a versatile flex area currently set up as a gym, catering to your active lifestyle. Additionally, an integral heated garage ensures that you won't have to brave the cold winter months. Easy access to shopping and restaurants. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity for comfortable, contemporary living.
